{"config": {"wide_screen_mode": true}, "header": {"template": "carmine", "title": {"tag": "plain_text", "content": "🛡️ 婴儿安全资讯日报 · 2026年06月24日 周三"}}, "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "🔍 晚间推送 · 新增 **5** 条紧急 + **3** 条重要 · 截至21:00"}}, {"tag": "column_set", "flex_mode": "none", "background_style": "default", "columns": [{"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "🚨 **紧急**\n5 项\n需立即行动"}}]}, {"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "📌 **提醒**\n3 项\n值得关注"}}]}, {"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "💡 **贴士**\n3 条\n1~2 岁适用"}}]}]}, {"tag": "hr"}, {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "🔴 **紧急安全警示** — 请立即检查"}}, {"tag": "column_set", "flex_mode": "none", "background_style": "grey", "columns": [{"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "**FDA调查婴儿肉毒杆菌爆发：Nara Organics全线召回有机婴儿配方奶粉 — 3例确诊、3州受影响**\nFDA · 06-13/14\n\nFDA与CDC联合加州公共卫生部调查多州婴儿肉毒杆菌爆发。3例确诊/疑似A型肉毒毒素感染（加州、宾州、华盛顿州），发病时间2026年4-5月，全部3例均食用Nara Organics婴儿配方奶粉。6月13日Nara Organics同意召回全部批次产品。该品牌在Target线上线下及Nara.com销售，不涉及中国市场。\n\n🩺 症状：便秘、喂养困难、头部控制力丧失、吞咽困难，可进展为呼吸困难甚至呼吸停止\n🛡️ 预防：立即停止使用Nara Organics婴儿配方奶粉；保留开封奶粉至少一个月供检测\n✅ 行动：如宝宝已食用并出现上述症状→立即就医；接触过奶粉的物品用热肥皂水清洗"}}]}]}, {"tag": "action", "actions": [{"tag": "button", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "📋 FDA 官方通告"}, "type": "danger", "url": "https://www.fda.gov/food/outbreaks-foodborne-illness/outbreak-investigation-infant-botulism-powdered-infant-formula-june-2026", "multi_url": {"url": "https://www.fda.gov/food/outbreaks-foodborne-illness/outbreak-investigation-infant-botulism-powdered-infant-formula-june-2026"}}]}, {"tag": "column_set", "flex_mode": "none", "background_style": "grey", "columns": [{"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "**CPSC召回CooCooBaby婴儿躺椅：窒息与跌落风险，违反婴儿睡眠产品强制标准**\nCPSC · 06-19\n\nCooCooBaby婴儿躺椅（Baby Loungers）因违反婴儿睡眠产品强制安全标准被召回。产品存在严重窒息和跌落风险，可能导致婴儿死亡。消费者应立即停止使用并联系品牌退款。\n\n🩺 症状：婴儿在躺椅中可能翻身导致口鼻被遮挡→窒息；可能从躺椅跌落→头部外伤\n🛡️ 预防：婴儿睡眠应使用符合安全标准的婴儿床，不使用躺椅作为睡眠替代品\n✅ 行动：立即停用CooCooBaby婴儿躺椅→联系品牌办理退款"}}]}]}, {"tag": "action", "actions": [{"tag": "button", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "📋 CPSC 召回详情"}, "type": "danger", "url": "https://www.cpsc.gov/Recalls/2026/CooCooBaby-Baby-Loungers-Recalled-Due-to-Risk-of-Serious-Injury-or-Death-from-Suffocation-and-Fall-Hazards-Violates-Mandatory-Standard-for-Infant-Sleep-Products", "multi_url": {"url": "https://www.cpsc.gov/Recalls/2026/CooCooBaby-Baby-Loungers-Recalled-Due-to-Risk-of-Serious-Injury-or-Death-from-Suffocation-and-Fall-Hazards-Violates-Mandatory-Standard-for-Infant-Sleep-Products"}}]}, {"tag": "column_set", "flex_mode": "none", "background_style": "grey", "columns": [{"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "**CPSC召回GOPO拉绳磨牙玩具：窒息风险，违反玩具强制安全标准**\nCPSC · 06-19\n\nGOPO Toys召回拉绳式磨牙玩具（Pull String Teething Toys），产品含有小零件且拉绳过长，存在严重窒息甚至死亡风险。违反玩具强制安全标准。消费者应立即停止使用。\n\n🩺 症状：拉绳过长可能缠绕婴儿颈部→勒颈窒息；小零件脱落→气道阻塞窒息\n🛡️ 预防：选择磨牙玩具时确认无小零件、拉绳长度<7cm，检查3C认证\n✅ 行动：立即停用GOPO拉绳磨牙玩具→检查家中所有磨牙玩具的安全性"}}]}]}, {"tag": "action", "actions": [{"tag": "button", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "📋 CPSC 召回详情"}, "type": "danger", "url": "https://www.cpsc.gov/Recalls/2026/GOPO-Toys-Recalls-Pull-String-Teething-Toys-Due-to-Risk-of-Serious-Injury-or-Death-from-Choking-Violate-Mandatory-Standard-for-Toys", "multi_url": {"url": "https://www.cpsc.gov/Recalls/2026/GOPO-Toys-Recalls-Pull-String-Teething-Toys-Due-to-Risk-of-Serious-Injury-or-Death-from-Choking-Violate-Mandatory-Standard-for-Toys"}}]}, {"tag": "column_set", "flex_mode": "none", "background_style": "grey", "columns": [{"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "**CPSC召回BABESIDE娃娃与推车玩具：小零件窒息风险，违反小型部件禁令**\nCPSC · 06-19\n\nBABESIDE品牌娃娃与推车儿童玩具因含有小零件被召回，存在严重窒息甚至死亡风险。产品通过HYBDOLLS店铺在Amazon销售，违反小型部件禁令。消费者应立即停止使用。\n\n🩺 症状：玩具小零件脱落被婴幼儿误吞→气道阻塞→窒息\n🛡️ 预防：购买玩具前做\"卫生纸卷筒测试\"：能塞入卷筒的小零件有窒息风险\n✅ 行动：立即停用BABESIDE娃娃推车玩具→远离3岁以下婴幼儿"}}]}]}, {"tag": "action", "actions": [{"tag": "button", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "📋 CPSC 召回详情"}, "type": "danger", "url": "https://www.cpsc.gov/Recalls/2026/BABESIDE-Doll-and-Stroller-Childrens-Toys-Recalled-Due-to-Risk-of-Serious-Injury-or-Death-from-Choking-Hazard-Violate-Small-Parts-Ban-Sold-on-Amazon-by-HYBDOLLS", "multi_url": {"url": "https://www.cpsc.gov/Recalls/2026/BABESIDE-Doll-and-Stroller-Childrens-Toys-Recalled-Due-to-Risk-of-Serious-Injury-or-Death-from-Choking-Hazard-Violate-Small-Parts-Ban-Sold-on-Amazon-by-HYBDOLLS"}}]}, {"tag": "column_set", "flex_mode": "none", "background_style": "grey", "columns": [{"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "**CPSC召回Joolz Aer2婴儿车适配器：跌倒/受伤风险**\nCPSC · 06-19\n\nJoolz召回Aer2婴儿车汽车安全座椅适配器（Car Seat Adapters），适配器可能意外脱落导致婴儿跌倒受伤。消费者应停止使用并联系品牌更换。\n\n🩺 症状：安全座椅适配器脱落→婴儿连同安全座椅从推车坠落→头部/身体外伤\n🛡️ 预防：每次安装安全座椅适配器时检查卡扣是否完全锁定，听到\"咔嗒\"声确认\n✅ 行动：立即停用Joolz Aer2适配器→联系Joolz免费更换"}}]}]}, {"tag": "action", "actions": [{"tag": "button", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "📋 CPSC 召回详情"}, "type": "danger", "url": "https://www.cpsc.gov/Recalls/2026/Joolz-Recalls-Aer2-Car-Seat-Adapters-for-Strollers-Due-to-Risk-of-Serious-Injury-from-Fall-Hazard", "multi_url": {"url": "https://www.cpsc.gov/Recalls/2026/Joolz-Recalls-Aer2-Car-Seat-Adapters-for-Strollers-Due-to-Risk-of-Serious-Injury-from-Fall-Hazard"}}]}, {"tag": "hr"}, {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "🟡 **重要安全提醒** — 值得关注"}}, {"tag": "column_set", "flex_mode": "none", "background_style": "grey", "columns": [{"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "**1. Veseacky儿童睡衣套装召回：严重烧伤风险，违反联邦阻燃强制标准**\n　　CPSC · 06-19\n　　Veseacky品牌儿童睡衣套装因违反美国联邦儿童睡衣可燃性标准（16 CFR 1615/1616）被召回，存在严重烧伤甚至死亡风险。消费者应立即停用并联系品牌全额退款。\n\n**2. SHEIN召回Michley儿童睡衣：烧伤风险，违反联邦阻燃标准**\n　　CPSC · 06-19\n　　SHEIN旗下Michley品牌儿童睡衣因违反联邦儿童睡衣可燃性标准被召回。产品在接触火源时可能迅速燃烧，造成严重烧伤或死亡。消费者应立即停用。\n\n**3. 中国造纸学会就纸尿裤甲酰胺事件声明：市面在售产品安全可控，报道检测信息缺失**\n　　中国造纸学会 · 06-19\n　　针对《经济参考报》6月18日报道好奇、碧芭宝贝、Babycare等纸尿裤检出甲酰胺，中国造纸学会声明：报道未披露检测方法、数值、机构等核心信息，不具备科学依据；涉事品牌已委托CMA资质第三方检测均未检出甲酰胺。造纸学会将组织行业甲酰胺风险专项自查。"}}]}]}, {"tag": "action", "actions": [{"tag": "button", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "📋 CPSC 原文"}, "type": "default", "url": "https://www.cpsc.gov/Recalls/2026/Veseacky-Pajama-Sets-Recalled-Due-to-Risk-of-Serious-Injury-or-Death-from-Burn-Hazard-Violate-Mandatory-Standards-for-Childrens-Sleepwear", "multi_url": {"url": "https://www.cpsc.gov/Recalls/2026/Veseacky-Pajama-Sets-Recalled-Due-to-Risk-of-Serious-Injury-or-Death-from-Burn-Hazard-Violate-Mandatory-Standards-for-Childrens-Sleepwear"}}, {"tag": "button", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "📋 CPSC 原文"}, "type": "default", "url": "https://www.cpsc.gov/Recalls/2026/SHEIN-Distribution-Corporation-Recalls-Michley-Childrens-Pajamas-Due-to-Risk-of-Serious-Injury-or-Death-from-Burn-Hazard-Violate-Mandatory-Standard-for-Childrens-Sleepwear", "multi_url": {"url": "https://www.cpsc.gov/Recalls/2026/SHEIN-Distribution-Corporation-Recalls-Michley-Childrens-Pajamas-Due-to-Risk-of-Serious-Injury-or-Death-from-Burn-Hazard-Violate-Mandatory-Standard-for-Childrens-Sleepwear"}}, {"tag": "button", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "📋 中国造纸学会 原文"}, "type": "default", "url": "https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1868422937374110920", "multi_url": {"url": "https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1868422937374110920"}}]}, {"tag": "hr"}, {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "📰 **品类覆盖** · 5 类活跃 · 8 类今日暂无新增"}}, {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "🍼婴幼儿食品  |  🧸启智玩具  |  👕服饰寝具  |  🚼出行安全  |  👶纸尿裤"}}, {"tag": "hr"}, {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "💡 **每日安全贴士** · 1~2 岁"}}, {"tag": "column_set", "flex_mode": "none", "background_style": "grey", "columns": [{"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "🍼 **奶粉安全自查** · 检查家中婴儿奶粉品牌及批次，关注FDA/市场监管总局召回公告；开封奶粉密封冷藏保存，4周内用完"}}]}]}, {"tag": "column_set", "flex_mode": "none", "background_style": "grey", "columns": [{"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "🛏️ **婴儿睡眠安全** · 1-2岁宝宝应睡在符合安全标准的婴儿床上，不使用躺椅/沙发作为睡眠替代品；床垫与护栏间缝隙不超过两指宽"}}]}]}, {"tag": "column_set", "flex_mode": "none", "background_style": "grey", "columns": [{"tag": "column", "width": "weighted", "weight": 1, "elements": [{"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "🧸 **磨牙玩具三查** · 一查拉绳长度<7cm，二查无小零件脱落风险，三查3C认证标志；GOPO召回警示"}}]}]}, {"tag": "hr"}, {"tag": "div", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "📱 以上为 8 条资讯摘要 · 完整图文请见下方"}}, {"tag": "action", "actions": [{"tag": "button", "text": {"tag": "lark_md", "content": "📖 查看完整图文日报"}, "type": "primary", "url": "https://cdaf7256d50347f2851c0b420371a376.app.codebuddy.work", "multi_url": {"url": "https://cdaf7256d50347f2851c0b420371a376.app.codebuddy.work"}}]}, {"tag": "hr"}, {"tag": "note", "elements": [{"tag": "lark_md", "content": "📡 FDA · CPSC · 中国造纸学会 · 市场监管总局 | ⚠️ 仅供参考 · 紧急情况请立即就医 | V9"}]}]}